Package: climatestripes
Type: Package
Title: A Simple Visual Depiction of a Temperature Variable and Climate Change
Version: 1.1
Author: Daniel E. Duplisea
Maintainer: Daniel Duplisea <daniel.duplisea@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
Description: Climate stripes and rings plots for visualising temperature time series and climate change.
    Stripes plots show temperature anomalies as coloured vertical bars over time. Rings plots show the
    same information in a circular tree-ring style. Both support superimposed data and trend lines.
    Includes tools for identifying structural breakpoints in the temperature trend.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    mgcv,
    scales,
    data.table,
    plotrix,
    segmented
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
